Terima kasih.

245
00:12:41,626 --> 00:12:42,666
Kalau begitu,

246
00:12:43,118 --> 00:12:44,847
mari kita mulai
membahas kasus ini.

247
00:12:46,132 --> 00:12:47,147
Baik.

248
00:12:51,855 --> 00:12:53,135
Dia memang aneh.

249
00:12:53,789 --> 00:12:56,759
Berdasarkan hasil otopsi,
