00:24:28,788 --> 00:24:30,321
Rincian panggilan
telepon juga ada.

425
00:24:30,938 --> 00:24:32,404
Alibinya sempurna.

426
00:24:32,813 --> 00:24:35,966
Apakah kau bersedia
menyerahkan ponsel?

427
00:24:36,462 --> 00:24:38,339
Tentu. Ambil saja.

428
00:24:44,148 --> 00:24:48,421
Tapi, Jung In-Yeong
menderita sindrom Korsakoff,

429
00:24:49,574 --> 00:24:50,608
apakah kau tidak tahu?

